cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about natural language processing and specifically semantic role labeling.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new neural network model for SRL.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper is about improving the performance of an AI system for natural language understanding.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper uses neural networks as the basis for their model.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper uses self-attention, a technique commonly used in computer vision, in their model.
